description: Welcome to 300 Pier 4 Blvd Unit 5C Seaport.This stunning rarely available luxurious C-unit with 3-bedrooms,2.5-bathrooms, front facing waterfront residence is surrounded by water.This meticulously designed residence boasts floor-to-ceiling windows with plenty of natural lighting with breathtaking harbor views.The open-concept living area is anchored by a sleek,custom electric fireplace creating a sophisticated ambiance perfect for both relaxation&entertaining.The kitchen is complete with Gaggenau appliances,&water fall quartz island.The primary suite features amazing water views,custom walk-in closet,glass-enclosed shower,dual vanity&tub.2nd bedroom  en-suite with water views.3rd bedroom can be used as great home office.Relax on the balcony overlooking the harbor.Amenities include 24-hour concierge,fitness center,golf simulator,residence lounge,outdoor terrace overlooking the water&grills.Enjoy Seaport finest restaurants,including Woods Hill Table,The Block at Woods Hill &Nautilus.
